        <div class="absolute right-12 top-40 vertical-text text-slate-300 text-6xl serif hidden lg:block select-none pointer-events-none" data-t="hero_vertical">
            細胞の時間を、美しく。
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl px-10 text-center z-10">
