                </h1>
                <p class="text-slate-700 leading-loose max-w-2xl mx-auto font-normal text-lg" data-t="hero_desc">
                    當細胞能量與修復機制處於和諧狀態，時間便不再是威脅。<br>我們致力於讓每一顆細胞，都擁有抵禦時間的力量。
                </p>
                <div class="mt-12">
                    <a href="#programs" class="inline-block px-12 py-4 bg-slate-900 text-white text-xs tracking-widest font-bold uppercase hover:bg-amber-800 transition duration-500 rounded-sm shadow-xl">探索管理計畫</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 科學啟示 (Science Section) -->
    <section id="science" class="relative py-36 px-10 bg-[#E9E5DE] overflow-hidden">
        <!-- 剪影背景: 波紋/山脈 (Silhouette 2) -->
        <svg class="silhouette-decor -bottom-10 -right-20 w-[800px] opacity-[0.04]" viewBox="0 0 1000 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M0,150 Q150,50 300,150 T600,150 T900,150 L1000,200 L0,200 Z" fill="#9E7A3D"/>
            <path d="M0,170 Q200,100 400,170 T800,170 L1000,200 L0,200 Z" fill="#9E7A3D" opacity="0.5"/>
        </svg>

        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-24 relative z-10">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 reveal">
                <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-amber-800/30 text-[10px] text-amber-900 font-bold mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">Nobel Prize Legacy</div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl serif text-slate-900 mb-10 leading-tight" data-t="science_title">源自 2009 年的<br>科學啟示</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-800 mb-8 leading-loose font-normal text-md" data-t="science_desc_1">
                    諾貝爾獎揭示了「端粒與端粒酶」的機制，正式開啟了人類與老化對話的新篇章。這不僅是生物學的突破，更是掌握生命長度的密碼。
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-800 leading-loose font-normal text-md" data-t="science_desc_2">
                    MitoActiveLife 站在這份遺產之上，將目光投向更深處的連結：端粒的修復需要龐大能量，而能量的源頭就在「粒線體」。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 reveal">
                <div class="bg-white p-14 soft-shadow text-center relative border border-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-1 bg-amber-800"></div>
                    <!-- 卡片內剪影: 圓形紋理 -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.1" stroke-dasharray="1 2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl serif mb-8 italic text-slate-900 leading-relaxed relative z-10" data-t="science_quote">「端粒是時鐘，<br>粒線體是電池。」</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium tracking-wide relative z-10" data-t="science_framework">
                        端粒防護 ‧ 粒線體供能 ‧ 腸道微生態
